ulations sampled over Europe, at neutral and candidate genes, has allowed to  evidence signatures of selection for Tnf, Mx2 and the Drb Mhc class II genes.  Altogether, these results corroborated the hypothesis of an evolution of tolerance strategies in rodents. We finally discuss the importance of these results from the medical and  epidemiological perspectives.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Charbonnel, Nathalie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pag\u00e8s, Marie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sironen, Tarja", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Henttonen, Heikki", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vapalahti, Olli", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mustonen, Jukka", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vaheri, Antti", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["<i>Puumala</i> virus", "hantavirus", "hosts", "immunity-related genes", "interaction", "reservoirs", "rodents", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/3ca31f5ce48f2d53c253b34108d53f1a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d3ed0779d19e8d78462885df94f9f7a5e021b9f74d505f83e17ea504265fc9d9", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/5SGMKXMA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/5SGMKXMA", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/497b52c02240a6571c0c66936e92b36b!/b358831-361397", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journa